"order-2 mt-5 w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><img class="m-auto w-full" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2H5C4DQQVRW4WMQ45MJ5ED/images-3.fill.size_245x184.v1714664921.jpg" alt="谷歌 Pixel 7a (128GB)（已解锁）" width="245" height="184" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-2 mt-2 hidden w-64 md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:block"><img class="m-auto w-full" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HF2H5C4DQQVRW4WMQ45MJ5ED/images-3.fill.size_245x184.v1714664921.jpg" alt="谷歌 Pixel 7a (128GB)（已解锁）" width="245" height="184" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-5 w-full"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="py-auto flex h-full w-full flex-col justify-center rounded-md bg-brand-green text-center font-sans text-base text-white md:text-sm"><div>获得优惠</div></div></div></div><div class="mx-2 mt-2 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-xs font-medium md:text-xs">伍特</span><span class="text-sm font-bold md:text-sm">339.99 美元</span></div><div class="my-0 text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-xs font-bold line-through md:text-xs">$499.00</span><span class="text-sm font-bold text-brand-green md:text-sm">节省 $159.01</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p> Pixel 7a 具有与 Pixel 7 类似的金属边框设计，但它略小、更轻，屏幕为 6.1 英寸，比 Pixel 7 的 6.3 英寸。背面也由光滑的塑料背面制成，而不是采用 Pixel 7 的 Gorilla Glass Victus 材料，带来更优质的感觉。相机各不相同，但<a href="https://www.digitaltrends.com/mobile/google-pixel-7-vs-pixel-7a-camera-test-comparison/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="（在新窗口中打开）">没有明显的“更好”</a> 。</p><p>以实惠的价格购买高端 Android 手机的用户应该认真考虑这两款 Pixel 手机。未来几年<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/january-pixel-security-update" target="_blank">，谷歌持续的安全更新</a>和<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/whats-new-january-pixel-features-drop" target="_blank">Pixel 功能更新</a>将涵盖这三者。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/google-pixel-7-deal<dc:creator>丹尼尔·奥罗佩萨</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category></item><item><title>通过更改这八个设置让 Apple Notes 变得更好</title><guid ispermalink="false">01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB</guid><pubDate> Thu, 02 May 2024 18:39:00 +0000</pubDate><description>每个注释不必以巨大的标题开头。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/hero-image.jpg"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://lifehacker.com/how-to-use-apple-notes-to-have-secret-chats-with-others-1849112538" target="_blank">Apple Notes 是一款很棒的应用程序，</a>可以用来记下你的想法。它随您的<a href="https://lifehacker.com/45-of-lifehackers-favorite-iphone-hacks-of-2022-1849920815" target="_blank">iPhone</a>一起提供，可在 Apple 设备之间可靠地同步， <a href="https://lifehacker.com/9-of-the-best-but-hidden-notes-app-features-on-your-i-1850076909" target="_blank">具有共享等出色功能</a>，最重要的是，它是免费的。即便如此，仍有许多您可能不知道的简单方法可以改进应用程序。</p><h2>并非每个笔记都需要标题</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-1.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示更改新笔记开始方式的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-1.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-1.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-1.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p>默认情况下，每个笔记中的第一行都会自动采用标题格式，这意味着它将是粗体并使用大字体。有些人喜欢这个，但如果您想使用不同的字体大小，请转到<strong>“设置”>;“笔记”>;“新笔记开头”</strong> 。您可以选择以<strong>标题</strong>、<strong>副标题</strong>或<strong>正文</strong>文本开始笔记，而不是标题。对于正常大小的单词，正文是正确的选择。另外两个设置可让您在每个注释的开头保留标题，但与默认值相比，字体大小较小。</p><h2>更改清单的排序方式</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-2.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示自动对清单进行排序的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-2.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-2.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-2.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p>您可以使用 Apple Notes 制作清单，如果您使用该应用程序创建共享待办事项列表或购物清单，这会非常有用。默认情况下，当您在这些列表中勾选某个项目时，Notes 会将其保留在原处。有些人喜欢将已完成的项目移动到列表底部，您可以通过转到<strong>“设置”>;“注释”>;“对勾选项目排序”</strong>并选择<strong>“自动”</strong>来设置。</p><h2>使用不同的背景颜色</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-3.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示更改背景颜色的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-3.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-3.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-3.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p> Apple 不允许您为 Notes 选择自定义背景颜色，但您仍然有几个选择。如果您的手机处于<a href="https://lifehacker.com/how-to-enable-dark-mode-in-ios-and-android-1841770858" target="_blank">深色模式</a>，您仍然可以强制笔记使用白色背景。这对于一般喜欢深色模式但发现在白色背景下阅读文本更容易的人来说非常有用。通过转到<strong>“设置”>;“笔记”>;“笔记背景”</strong>并选择<strong>“浅色”</strong>来进行此调整。如果您在手机上使用浅色模式，则根本不会出现此选项 - 它仅适用于启用了深色模式的用户。</p><h2>选择用于手写的线条或网格</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-4.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示使用网格进行手写的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-4.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-4.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-4.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p> Apple Notes 允许您使用手写笔手写笔记，但默认设置在您开始书写时显示空白页。如果您喜欢带格子的笔记本，请转到<strong>“设置”>;“笔记”>;“线条和网格”</strong>并进行选择。</p><h2>让排序为您服务</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-5.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示以不同方式对笔记进行排序的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-5.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-5.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-5.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p> Apple Notes 的默认排序选项很好，但如果您喜欢其他选项，您仍然可以进行更改。转到<strong>“设置”>;“注释”</strong> ，然后向下滚动到<strong>“查看”</strong>部分。如果您不喜欢按日期分组的笔记，您可以禁用该选项，但我不建议这样做。您还可以选择<strong>笔记排序依据</strong>并选择<strong>创建日期</strong>或<strong>标题</strong>。每次您对旧笔记进行更改时，前者将停止对笔记进行重新排序，而后者将按字母顺序对笔记进行排序。</p><h2>以图库形式查看您的笔记</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-6.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示以图库形式查看笔记的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-6.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-6.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-6.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p>如果您厌倦了以基于文本的列表形式查看笔记，可以切换到图库视图。有些人觉得画廊视图更容易浏览，而另一些人则喜欢它，因为它美观。通过打开 iPhone 上的 Notes 应用程序并点击右上角的<strong>三点</strong>图标来进行切换。选择<strong>“以图库查看”</strong>进行切换。</p><h2>在 iPhone 上记一些笔记</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-7.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示使用离线笔记帐户的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-7.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-7.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-7.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p>您可能会将所有笔记与云中的帐户相关联，这在设备之间切换时很方便。但如果您想在一台设备上（例如您的 iPhone）专门保存一些笔记，您也可以这样做。前往<strong>“设置”>;“便笺”</strong>并启用<strong>“在我的 iPhone 上”帐户</strong>。这将在 Apple Notes 中显示一个新文件夹：此文件夹中的注释不会出现在其他设备上。但是，如果您为 iCloud 启用了 Notes，则此文件夹将包含在 iPhone 的 iCloud 备份中。</p><h2>无论您身在何处，都可以拥抱笔记</h2><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-8.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg" alt="Apple Notes 设置的屏幕截图，显示了调整锁定屏幕笔记的选项。" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-8.fill.size_800x450.v1714655390.jpg 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-8.fill.size_1400x788.v1714655390.jpg 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HWWP08MMCZQNQYQMWWHXKJAB/images-8.fill.size_2000x1125.v1714655390.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：Pranay Parab</span></div></div><p>如果您添加应用程序TOI控制中心，则iPhone允许您从iPhone（包括锁定屏幕）（包括锁定屏幕）访问笔记。只需转到<strong>设置>;控制中心</strong>并添加<strong>注释</strong>即可。现在，当您从控制中心打开应用程序时，它将自动打开新的音符。您还可以使应用程序打开您的最新音符。为此，请转到<strong>“设置”>;“注释”>;“ lock屏幕上的访问说明”</strong> ，然后选择<strong>“简历”最后一张</strong>。</p><hr><p>在新iPhone的市场上？查看以下最新选项：</p><ul><li><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/6Xe1k?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=iPhone%2015&amp;short_url=6Xe1k&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">iPhone 15</a></p></li><li><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/pgw0Z?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=iPhone%2015%20Plus&amp;short_url=pgw0Z&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">iPhone 15 Plus</a></p></li><li><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/5MJPN?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=iPhone%2015%20Pro&amp;short_url=5MJPN&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">iPhone 15 专业版</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://zdcs.link/KJ1rG?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=iPhone%2015%20Pro%20Max&amp;short_url=KJ1rG&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">iPhone 15 Pro 最大</a></p></li></ul>]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/tech/make-apple-notes-better-by-changing-shanging-phistings<dc:creator>帕拉奈·帕拉</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category></item></channel></rss>